msgstr "Linked Discourses 52 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: 2. Dutiyavagga → sahassavaggo (bj)
msgctxt "sn52.11:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. A Thousand "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 11. Kappasahassasutta → sahassasuttaṃ (bj) | sahassa (pts1)
msgctxt "sn52.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Kappasahassasutta "
msgstr "11. A Thousand Eons "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn52.11:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā anuruddho sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time Venerable Anuruddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

msgctxt "sn52.11:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho sambahulā bhikkhū yenāyasmā anuruddho tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā anuruddhena saddhiṃ … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho te bhikkhū āyasmantaṃ anuruddhaṃ etadavocuṃ: "
msgstr "Then several mendicants went up to Venerable Anuruddha, exchanged greetings with him … and said: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn52.11:2.1"
msgid "“Katamesaṃ āyasmā anuruddho dhammānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā mahābhiññataṃ patto”ti? "
msgstr "“What things has Venerable Anuruddha developed and cultivated to attain great direct knowledge?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn52.11:2.2"
msgid "“Catunnaṃ khvāhaṃ, āvuso, satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā mahābhiññataṃ patto. "
msgstr "“Reverends, I attained great direct knowledge by developing and cultivating the four kinds of mindfulness meditation. "

msgctxt "sn52.11:2.3"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn52.11:2.4"
msgid "Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, kāye kāyānupassī viharāmi … pe … "
msgstr "I meditate observing an aspect of the body … "

msgctxt "sn52.11:2.5"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe … "
msgstr "feelings … "

msgctxt "sn52.11:2.6"
msgid "citte … pe … "
msgstr "mind … "

msgctxt "sn52.11:2.7"
msgid "dhammesu dhammānupassī viharāmi ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ—"
msgstr "principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. "

msgctxt "sn52.11:2.8"
msgid "imesaṃ khvāhaṃ, āvuso, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā mahābhiññataṃ patto. "
msgstr "I attained great direct knowledge by developing and cultivating these four kinds of mindfulness meditation. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn52.11:2.9"
msgid "Imesañca panāhaṃ, āvuso, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā kappasahassaṃ anussarāmī”ti. "
msgstr "And it’s because of developing and cultivating these four kinds of mindfulness meditation that I recollect a thousand eons.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn52.11:2.10"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

